      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable vehicle with plenty of life left? This car is in honest, fair condition and has been a reliable companion on the road. While it shows some typical signs of wear and tear consistent with its age, it remains a solid choice for anyone seeking functional transportation at a great value. It\u2019s ready for its next chapter with a new owner who appreciates a car with character!",
