    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit delivers linear power delivery through individual throttle bodies and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains composed with a factory limited-slip differential and reinforced rear subframe mounting points\u2014a critical preventative measure already addressed. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and valve clearance adjustment, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates within factory specifications. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains robust and engagement remains sharp.",
      "price": 34500.0,
